@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ohbrbe(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (0.22 / (0.83 * (v2 + 0.53 + v1 + 0.16)))
    v2 = v0
    v0 = 0.50
    v1 = wp.cos((0.44 - v1))
    v0 = v0
    tmp = ((0.79 + (tmp + 0.17 * v2 + 0.26)) - 0.31)
    data[tid] = v0
